    "body": "## Problem\nvim.loader.find don't include module under package.{,c}path\nso byte cache won't work for module from luarocks\n\n\n## Solution\nenhance vim.loader.find with package.searchpath\n\nOriginally I find lua ftplugin gf don't work well with package.path,\nthen I think more direct to fix here.\n",
