        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "My experience is much closer to @echasnovski's (~30% startup time reduction on a hot loader cache) than @lewis6991's. The savings really depend on your plugin collection -- both number and specific choice. (My feelings about luarocks are well-known, though, so I won't comment on the change in this PR.)",
